---
title: Cheesy Capsicum Chicken & Herby Root Veg with Garlic Butter Broccoli
description: Load up chicken thigh with flavour before baking them until golden and tender. Chargrilled capsicum relish and melted Cheddar combine to make a sensational topping that everyone will happily devour!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67b839387f7b48609c8b1846-fb59bc73.jpeg
